  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "tx"
   },
   "html": "\n<div><span class=\"m_b\">引用</span>陸軍切っての教養といわれる知性派であり、\n日露戦争後の大尉時代、<a href=\"../p/yaritomo.html\">山縣有朋</a>の副官でありながら、長州閥にも、どの派閥にも属さない孤高で剛毅の将軍である。</div>\n<div class=\"txr\"><a href=\"../text/mk_gunji.html\">升本喜年 「軍人の最期」</a>\n　Ｐ．１９５<span class=\"book\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2581%25AE%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%259C%259F%25E2%2580%2595%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B0%2586%25E8%25BB%258D%25E3%2581%25AE%25E7%2594%259F%25E3%2581%258D%25E3%2581%2596%25E3%2581%25BE%25E3%2581%25A8%25E3%2581%259D%25E3%2581%25AE%25E6%25AD%25BB\" target=\"_blank\">この本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></span></div>\n"
  },
